attributes.title: Face Jam’s Truck’d Up! | Official Trailer
attributes.caption: In this kitchen battle, four teams of two will try to accurately recreate culinary copies of fast food classics in a food truck in the allotted time. While the teams are cooking in the hot trucks, our expert Face Jam judges will monitor the cooking process and commentate on the goings-on in the kitchen. After the big cook, the teams will present their dishes to Face Jam for tasting and critique. Over the course of the season, we’ll find out who’s best in the kitchen and be crowned champion.
